Ribbed track-cover plates (Kettenabdeckbleche) are fitted over the tracks; their front and rear ends can be folded up for driving over cratered ground (Trichtergelände).
4. Motor  -  Engine
The engine is rubber-mounted at three points (dreifach in Gummi gelagert): at the front on two support trunnions (Tragzapfen), and at the rear on a cross-member (Querträger) that can pivot about the crank axle (Kurbelachse).

